2004-04-25  Sebastian Rahtz  <rahtz@spqr-dell.oucs.ox.ac.uk>

	* add translate-instance.xsl: converts elements and attributes in 
	a TEI P5 XML document to the chosen language.

	* add translate-odd.xsl: extends a TEI extension written in ODD to
	use element and attribute names from the chosen language

	* teinames.xml: removed quite a few cases where the translated
	name was no different to the english one

